Eating Inn are part of The Great British Pub Card. At our Eating Inn pubs ? across England and Scotland ? you?ll always enjoy delicious dishes and great value.        Whether you?re looking for a quick bite to eat or celebrating a special occasion, our teams will be delighted to welcome you in style. The Great British Pub Card is the leading pub gift card that can be redeemed against food, drink or accommodation in over 3000 locations nationwide. Including brands such as Chef & Brewer, Loch Fyne, Flaming Grill, Hungry Horse and many others. The Great British Pub Card is also available to purchase as a digital code, its flexible and offers a vast choice of food, drink or dining opportunities. Perfect for celebrating those special times with family, catching-up with friends or meeting with colleagues. For more information visit www.greatbritishpubcard.co.uk.